---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Security Awareness Training | Huntress Managed SAT — Blue Cap IT" description="Huntress Managed Security Awareness Training reduces human risk with engaging, expert-backed training built on real-world threat intelligence. Hands-on simulations, phishing tests, and gamification — deployed by Blue Cap IT.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <img src="/Huntress/Huntress Primary Logo - Teal.png" alt="Huntress" style="max-height:50px;width:auto;margin-bottom:1.5rem;"/>
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="huntress.html">Huntress</a> <span>/</span> Security Awareness Training</div>
      <div class="section-label">Huntress Platform</div>
      <h1>Security Awareness <span class="grad">Training</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Your employees are your first line of defense — or your biggest vulnerability. Huntress Managed SAT turns them into an asset with engaging, expert-backed training built on real-world threat intelligence, hands-on tradecraft simulations, and gamification that makes cybersecurity concepts stick.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why Huntress SAT</div>
          <h2>Training That <span class="grad">Actually Works.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Most security awareness training is boring compliance checkbox content that employees click through and forget. Huntress SAT is different — built by cybersecurity experts and Emmy Award-winning animators, it uses real-world attack scenarios, hands-on simulations, and gamification to create genuine behavior change.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🎬</div>
            <div><h4>Emmy-Winning Content</h4><p>Training content created by Emmy Award-winning animators and cybersecurity experts. Engaging, memorable, and based on real-world threats — not dry compliance slides.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🎮</div>
            <div><h4>Hands-On Simulations</h4><p>Tradecraft simulations put employees in attackers' shoes — so they understand how phishing, social engineering, and credential theft actually work.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🎣</div>
            <div><h4>Phishing Simulations</h4><p>Realistic phishing tests based on current threat intelligence. Measure your team's susceptibility and track improvement over time.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">📈</div>
            <div><h4>Fully Managed</h4><p>Huntress cybersecurity experts develop, implement, and oversee your entire training program. You get results without the administrative overhead.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Training Topics</div>
        <h2>What Your Team <span class="grad">Will Learn</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));">
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🎣</div>
          <h3>Phishing &amp; Social Engineering</h3>
          <p>Recognize phishing emails, vishing calls, smishing texts, and social engineering tactics before falling for them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🔑</div>
          <h3>Password Security</h3>
          <p>Best practices for creating strong passwords, using password managers, and enabling multi-factor authentication.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">💻</div>
          <h3>Device Security</h3>
          <p>Securing laptops, phones, and personal devices. Safe browsing habits, software updates, and physical security awareness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">📁</div>
          <h3>Data Protection</h3>
          <p>Handling sensitive data, recognizing data exfiltration attempts, and understanding compliance responsibilities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <h2>Turn Your Team Into a <span class="grad">Security Asset</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:600px;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;text-align:center;">Contact Blue Cap IT to launch Huntress Security Awareness Training for your organization. We'll set up the program, manage the campaigns, and track your team's progress.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
